thread.title: Gary Schleuning
thread.title_full: Dyers RV reviewed by Gary Schleuning

author: Gary Schleuning
title: Gary Schleuning
text: Black tank is very strong and well made. Wish dimensions would have been a bit clearer. Outlet is not centered on bottom of tank therefore I had to trim one side of tank rim to get it to fit properly. Also wish there was a tank a bit longer but with same height and width that so would allow for more gallons of capacity. Overall a great product and would purchase again.
